  <section id="newgs-features">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="title">
        <h2>
            <small>Included Features</small>What's Included?
          </h2>
        <p>All the latest industry-standard features and more are here, ready for you and your friends to enjoy. Experience luxury gaming at budget prices on our extreme-performance hardware.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col col-lg-4">
          <div class="absolute-feature">
            <img src="/images/newgs-icon-mobile.svg" />
            <h4>Mega Factories Supported</h4>
            <p>Make our servers smoke, not your gaming rig. Custom turning on request by our support staff.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col col-lg-4">
          <div class="absolute-feature">
            <img src="/images/newgs-icon-plugins.svg" />
            <h4>Mod Support</h4>
            <p>Install and play any mods from Space Exploration or play hard mode with Bob's Mods.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col col-lg-4">
          <div class="absolute-feature">
            <img src="/images/newgs-icon-uptime.svg" />
            <h4><span class="numberfix">99.9%</span> Uptime Guarantee</h4>
            <p>High-availability means our game servers remain fully operational guaranteed.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col col-lg-4">
          <div class="absolute-feature">
            <img src="/images/newgs-icon-locations.svg" />
            <h4>Global Locations</h4>
            <p>Locations worldwide for the fastest gaming near you.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col col-lg-4"> 
          <div class="absolute-feature">
            <img src="/images/newgs-icon-hardware.svg" />
            <h4>Enterprise Hardware</h4>
            <p>The best hardware and networking equipment so you can play without worries.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col col-lg-4">
          <div class="absolute-feature">
            <img src="/images/newgs-icon-network.svg" />
            <h4>Dwarven Tunneling</h4>
            <p>All our game servers come equiped with gigabit networking standard.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col col-lg-4">
          <div class="absolute-feature">
            <img src="/images/newgs-icon-subdomain.svg" />
            <h4>Free Subdomain</h4>
            <p>Create a custom url for your friends to join your game through.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col col-lg-4">
          <div class="absolute-feature">
            <img src="/images/newgs-icon-budget.svg"/>
            <h4>Budget Friendly</h4>
            <p>Gaming at every price point, so no one is left out.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col col-lg-4">
          <div class="absolute-feature">
            <img src="/images/newgs-icon-ddos.svg" style="left:5px;"  />
            <h4>DDoS Protection</h4>
            <p>Our smart protection services keep you safe from all distributed denial-of-service threats.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="grey-bg no-bg-after" id="newgs-rows">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col col-lg-6">
          <h2>
              <small>ABOUT FACTORIO</small>About The Game
          </h2>
            <p>In the beginning, you will find yourself chopping trees, mining ores, crafting mechanical arms, and transport belts by hand. 
              Still, in a short time, you can become an industrial powerhouse with huge solar fields, oil refining and cracking, manufacturing 
              and deploying construction, and logistic robots, all for your resource needs.</p>
            <p> However, this heavy exploitation of the planet's resources 
              does not sit nicely with the locals, so you must be prepared to defend yourself and your machine empire. </p>
            <strong>In Factorio, the your base is in your hands!</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="col col-lg-5  ml-auto">
          <div class="newgs-game-feature check-feature mt-0">
            <img src="/images/game-check.svg" />
            <h5>Harvest Materials</h5>
            <p> Gather, transform, and utilize raw materials as you explore an uncharted world and endlessly automate production. </p>
          </div>
          <div class="newgs-game-feature check-feature">
            <img src="/images/game-check.svg" />
            <h5>Defend Against Biters</h5>
            <p> Fight the attacking biters trying to defend their home world from deforestation and rampant pollution. </p>
          </div>
          <div class="newgs-game-feature check-feature">
            <img src="/images/game-check.svg" />
            <h5>Build a Mega Factory</h5>
            <p> Build and expand the factory forever while trying to satiate the hungry beast within the factory walls, ever-consuming and continuously growing. </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </section>



      <div class="grey-dark-bg mt-n5">
