        </div>
        <div class="col col-lg-5 ml-auto">
          <h2 class="pt-4"><small>MOD SUPPORT</small>Support For All Mods</h2>
          <p>Expand your factory with new resources, machines, and more. If that doesn't cure your Factorio addiction, add in some space exploration and manage factories across multiple planets. </p>
          <a href="https://mods.factorio.com" target="_blank" class="button">View All Mods</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</div>

  <Map />
  <ThreeGuarantees />
  <GamePanel />
  <CompareTable />

  <section class="faq grey-bg" id="newgs-faq">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="flex-grid one">
        <div class="col">
          <h2>FAQ</h2>Have your own question? <a href="https://billing.aleforge.net/submitticket.php?step=2&deptid=1">Ask us here &raquo;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-grid two">
        <div class="col">
          <div class="toggle">
            <div class="toggle-title">
              <h3>
                  <i></i>
                  <span class="title-name">What is the difference between Standard and Premium?</span>
                </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="toggle-inner">
              <p>Standard was designed cost-effective for a small group of friends who want to play together. Premium is the best hardware we can source that runs at the fastest speeds, so your server will never lag or slow down. Each has its advantages and disadvantages.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- END OF TOGGLE -->
          <div class="toggle">
            <div class="toggle-title">
              <h3>
                  <i></i>
                  <span class="title-name">How do I know the best location to pick?</span>
                </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="toggle-inner">
              <p>You can use the <a href="#map">map</a> on this page above to show your real-time pings to each of our locations. Just refresh the page to recalculate your live latency.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- END OF TOGGLE -->
          <div class="toggle">
            <div class="toggle-title  ">
              <h3>
                  <i></i>
                  <span class="title-name"> Can I use mods, workshop content, or other custom resources on my server?</span>
                </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="toggle-inner">
              <p>Of course. For Factorio you will just need to upload the mods from your computer to the server. You can install whole mod packs with a click for other games, such as Minecraft.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- END OF TOGGLE -->
          <div class="toggle">
            <div class="toggle-title  ">
              <h3>
                  <i></i>
                  <span class="title-name"> Are the player slots adjustable?</span>
                </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="toggle-inner">
              <p>All Valheim plans are unlimited and you can change your slots via our control panel. We can recommended a number of slots based on your plans resources.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- END OF TOGGLE -->
        </div>
        <div class="col">
          <div class="toggle">
            <div class="toggle-title">
              <h3>
                  <i></i>
                  <span class="title-name">When will my server be set up?</span>
                </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="toggle-inner">
              <p>Once your order payment has been processed, the server will start installing and should be ready within a few minutes. If there are any unusual delays, don't hesitate to contact us with the details so we can correct any issues at once.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- END OF TOGGLE -->
          <div class="toggle">
            <div class="toggle-title ">
              <h3>
                  <i></i>
                  <span class="title-name">Do you provide DDoS protection?</span>
                </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="toggle-inner">
              <p>Yes, of course! Our automated systems tackle the brunt of these attackers but if you find yourself under attack let our staff know and they will make sure additional mitigators are put in place for your server.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- END OF TOGGLE -->
          <div class="toggle">
            <div class="toggle-title  ">
              <h3>
                  <i></i>
                  <span class="title-name"> Can I upgrade or downgrade my server?</span>
                </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="toggle-inner">
              <p>Yes. You can change your plan/resources at any time and your server will automatically have resources added or removed based on your choice.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- END OF TOGGLE -->
          <div class="toggle">
            <div class="toggle-title  ">
              <h3>
                  <i></i>
                  <span class="title-name"> Do you offer dedicated IPs?</span>
                </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="toggle-inner">
              <p>Yes, we have dedicated IPs available at checkout. Dedicated IPs are now an additional cost due to the increasing cost due to the IPV4 address shortage.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- END OF TOGGLE -->
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <SupportLinks />
  <Footer />
	</body>
